Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.15,0:08:15.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-也是唯一的希望  -那我们怎么去R层\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- She's our only hope. - How do we get down to Level R?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.08,0:08:17.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,楼梯井被封了  电梯又被丹尼尔控制着\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The stairwells are sealed shut and Daniel controls the elevator.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.30,0:08:19.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得再想办法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll have to improvise.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.04,0:08:23.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  给你这个  治你的偏头痛的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}By the way, these are for you, for your migraines.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.72,0:08:26.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加巴喷丁  你哪里...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Gabapentin. Where did you--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.89,0:08:30.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是苏勒玛尼博士用来治疗强迫症的  应该管用\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Dr. Sulemani used them for OCD. They should work.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.11,0:08:31.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要再用吗啡了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No more morphine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.06,0:08:34.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了吗  我需要你保持敏锐机警\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All right? I need you sharp.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.38,0:08:37.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在就剩下我们俩了  如果我们不同心协力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You and I are all we have left. If we don't have each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.38,0:08:39.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我们不互相帮助  我们就一无所有了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}if we don't back each other up, we have nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.80,0:08:42.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然了  还有...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Absolutely. And...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.69,0:08:44.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.92,0:08:48.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自助餐厅开放\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Cafeteria is now open.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.71,0:08:51.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自助餐厅开放\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Cafeteria is now open.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.43,0:08:53.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自助餐厅...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Cafeteria is now--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.02,0:09:23.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天哪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.37,0:09:27.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.27,0:09:29.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你的伤口  -感染了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Your wound. - Infection?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.94,0:09:33.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是  伤口愈合的非常快\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, it's... it's healing remarkably fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.35,0:09:36.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定是因为我基因好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Must have good genes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.77,0:09:38.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Must have.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.15,0:09:45.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.83,0:09:50.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么不告诉我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Why didn't you tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.87,0:09:52.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉你什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Tell you what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.56,0:09:55.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉我我出现幻觉了  杰伊不是真的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That I was hallucinating! That Jaye wasn't real.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.50,0:09:58.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么要让我继续相信她的存在\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Why did you let me go on believing she was here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.34,0:10:00.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很喜欢看别人受罪煎熬吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Do you enjoy watching people suffer?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.27,0:10:02.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟你一样  也是名医生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I am a doctor first, like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.84,0:10:04.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的责任是救死扶伤\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My job is to save people.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.77,0:10:05.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用撒谎救死扶伤吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}By lying to them?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.86,0:10:08.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没告诉你是因为没这个必要\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I didn't tell you, because I didn't need to.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.54,0:10:11.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你当时不知所措\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You were disoriented,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.26,0:10:14.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟杰伊说话好像对你有所帮助\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and speaking to Jaye seemed to be helping.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.94,0:10:19.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.59,0:10:22.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说得对\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.19,0:10:27.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救命啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.22,0:10:29.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救命\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.30,0:10:30.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.17,0:10:33.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并不是谁都有机会得救的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Not everyone can be saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.89,0:10:38.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沃克博士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Dr. Walker?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.99,0:10:40.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茱莉亚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Julia!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.92,0:10:42.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茱莉亚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Julia.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.49,0:10:52.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很久没做过铝热剂了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's been a long time since I've made thermite.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.88,0:10:55.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上次做还是高中做恶作剧的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It was in high school - senior prank.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.08,0:10:59.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然过程不是很顺利\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It didn't go very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.14,0:11:24.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里没设置隔离带\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This was no quarantine;
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.23,0:11:26.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像是被遗忘的尘封区域\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}it was a "seal and forget."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.19,0:11:33.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里面很暗  我看不太清楚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Dark in there. I can't see much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.08,0:11:35.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们可能全挤在实验室里了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They're probably all huddled in the labs.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.07,0:11:36.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样肯定找不着她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We'll never find her like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.06,0:11:39.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们得进去看看\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We have to go inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.62,0:11:53.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好像看见有什么人站在走廊那头\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I think I see something at the end of the hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.80,0:12:19.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快跑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.35,0:12:26.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-让我看看  -艾伦  不用  我没事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Come here. - Alan, stop. I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.52,0:12:28.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果有任何擦伤或者创口之类的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If there's an abrasion or a cut or anything of the kind--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.65,0:12:30.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-真没事  -我们得确保无虞  你明白的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- I'm fine. - We have to make sure. You know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.04,0:12:32.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真是没想到有这么多人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I had no idea there'd be so many of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.47,0:12:34.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你面临这么大的危险  我真是昏头了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I ought to have my head examined for putting you at risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.50,0:12:35.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我自愿跟着你下来的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I chose to go down there with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.83,0:12:37.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着  先是朵琳  现在又是茱尔斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Listen, first Doreen, then Jules.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.70,0:12:39.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不能再失去你了  莎拉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I can't lose you too, Sarah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.67,0:12:46.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茱莉亚的事我们要怎么办\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}what are we gonna do about Julia?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.61,0:12:51.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了找到她  我们得先对付那些...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}To get to her, we have to go through those...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.41,0:12:55.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-那些怪物  -我想说"那些患者"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Those monsters? - I was going to say "those patients."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.21,0:12:58.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危重患者  我们要想帮助茱尔斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}desperately sick patients. If we want to get to Jules,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.98,0:13:00.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们得先治好他们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}we'll have to treat them first.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.54,0:13:01.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是治不好呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What if we can't?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.79,0:13:04.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那上头就得连同我们一起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Then they'll bury this base...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.66,0:13:06.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将这基地彻底摧毁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}with us in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.74,0:13:18.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你干什么呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.59,0:13:22.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你昏过去了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You passed out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.09,0:13:25.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别担心  茱莉亚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Don't worry, Julia.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.05,0:13:28.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用不了多久我就能治好你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We'll have you back on your feet in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.99,0:13:35.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你照我眼睛做什么  我看不清了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What are you doing to my eyes? I can't see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.64,0:13:41.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.23,0:13:45.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要给你打镇静剂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm giving you a sedative.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.79,0:14:05.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你需要休息\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You should sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.71,0:14:07.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想睡过去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't want to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.90,0:14:08.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Shh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.69,0:14:12.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会好起来的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're going to be OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.05,0:15:05.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准许进入\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Access granted.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.13,0:15:30.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Aw! What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.81,0:15:49.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你是谁  -我还想问你呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Who are you? - I could ask you the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.49,0:15:51.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是阿娜娜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm Anana.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.26,0:15:53.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿娜娜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Anana?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.28,0:15:55.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这是在哪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.59,0:15:57.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在我家里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're in my home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.81,0:16:02.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非得铐起来吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Are these really necessary?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.13,0:16:04.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鬼知道你是谁呀\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Don't know you from Adam.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.69,0:16:06.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要换了是我  没准也会把你铐起来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}In that case, maybe I should cuff you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.17,0:16:10.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫塞尔西奥\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm Sergio.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.14,0:16:13.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我估计着我脸上这一拳是拜你所赐\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I assume I have you to thank for punching me in the face?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.34,0:16:15.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一个劲地打我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You kept trying to fight me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.43,0:16:17.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你感觉怎么样了  赛尔西奥\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How are you feeling otherwise,Sergio?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.24,0:16:18.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕透顶\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Like hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.23,0:16:19.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那也比被扔在雪地里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's better than expected for a guy
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.39,0:16:20.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等着被冻死要强得多\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}who was left for dead on the ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.20,0:16:23.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-这绿乎乎的是什么玩意  -这是海藻药膏\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- What is this green shit? - It's a seaweed pack.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.07,0:16:27.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这附近又找不着什么神医  所以将就着吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're not exactly near the Mayo Clinic, so relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.70,0:16:29.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是个警察\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're the law?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.61,0:16:33.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是汤拉尔定居点周围四百英里以内的的治安官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Only peace officer within 400 miles of Tonrar settlement.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.34,0:16:37.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-汤拉尔吗  -意思是"恶鬼"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Tonrar? - Means "Ghost."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.95,0:16:39.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实没有名字说的这么吓人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sounds scarier than what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.25,0:16:41.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不在一个地点停留太久\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We don't stay in one place very long.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.47,0:16:44.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给  喝了这个  能让你暖和点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Here, drink this. It'll warm you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.81,0:16:46.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你手指头没冻掉真是运气太好...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're lucky to have all your fingers and--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.28,0:16:51.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这是想干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What'd you have to do that for,huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.54,0:16:53.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是尽了地主之谊呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I was trying to be hospitable.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.94,0:16:56.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-疼  -疼就对了  正好让你明白状况\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- It hurts. - Good! Let that be our introduction.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.31,0:16:57.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你见鬼去吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Bullshit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.27,0:16:59.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-怎么着  你想拿我当人质吗  -看情况\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- What am I, a hostage? - Depends.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.96,0:17:01.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,局面会有多难看  全在你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This can be as dirty as you want it to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.23,0:17:05.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你想要什么  -要你脑袋里的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- What do you want? - I want what's in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.73,0:17:07.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉我所有关于北极生物公司的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Tell me what you know about Arctic Biosystems.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.85,0:17:09.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我什么都不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't know anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.59,0:17:10.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想这么玩吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's how you want to play it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.45,0:17:13.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那好  或许你就该是人质\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All right, then maybe you are a hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.68,0:17:18.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-真是荒唐  -如果你配合  那是最好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- This is ridiculous! - If you want to talk, great.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.13,0:17:20.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不  我总有办法把你带回基地\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If not, I can always bring you back to the base
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.82,0:17:23.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让那些想杀你的人了结你  有始有终\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and let whoever tried to kill you finish off what they started.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.94,0:17:31.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莎拉  来看这个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sarah...come have a look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.35,0:17:37.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说说你看到了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Tell me what you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.02,0:17:44.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,病毒在侵害细胞  迅速繁殖\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The virus is attacking the cell, multiplying rapidly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.73,0:17:48.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再看看  仔细看\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Look again. Look more closely.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.56,0:17:54.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天哪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, my god.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.66,0:17:56.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前我居然没发现\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I can't believe I didn't see it before.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.14,0:17:59.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么能发现呢  我们根本没注意这方面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How could you have? We weren't looking for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.72,0:18:01.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他把病毒用作运载机制\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He's using the virus as a delivery mechanism.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.86,0:18:04.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问题是  病毒对基因组有什么影响\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The question is: what's the virus bringing to the party?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.86,0:18:07.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原因又是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.14,0:18:12.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狗娘养的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Son of a bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.92,0:18:25.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-法拉格特博士  -病毒里有什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Dr. Farragut. - What's in the virus?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.11,0:18:28.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-什么也没有  -我亲眼看到了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Nothing. - I saw it with my own eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.43,0:18:30.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在基因序列中加入了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What did you splice into its genetic code?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.33,0:18:31.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听不懂你在说什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't know what you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.66,0:18:34.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你把病毒用作运载机制\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I know you're using the virus as a delivery mechanism.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.12,0:18:37.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉我  你乱用的是哪种基因疗法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now, what kind of gene therapy are you messing with?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.43,0:18:43.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你把我弟弟当成了小白鼠\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You used my brother as a lab rat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.24,0:18:45.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你搞砸了他的生活  茱莉亚的生活\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You played with his life, with Julia's life,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.76,0:18:47.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还搞砸了R层那些可怜人的生活\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}with the rest of those poor people on Level R.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.79,0:18:50.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你把基地建在这儿就没人能监管你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You put this place here so you wouldn't be regulated,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.23,0:18:52.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后你就可以扮演上帝来操控别人的生活\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}so you could play God with people's lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.20,0:18:54.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看你带来的后果吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Look where's it's gotten you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.70,0:18:56.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉我真相\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Tell me the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.16,0:19:05.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  纳尔维克的确是个运载系统\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes...NARVIK is a... delivery system.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.83,0:19:08.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但法拉格特博士  这并不是阴谋\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But there is no conspiracy, Dr. Farragut.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.57,0:19:10.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阴谋论只是你幻想出来的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That, I'm afraid, is in your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.33,0:19:16.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至于你弟弟...他也不是小白鼠\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}As far as your brother... he was no lab rat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.50,0:19:19.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那这到底是怎么回事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What then? What is all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.99,0:19:23.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是治疗绝症的一种方式\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A way to treat what was once untreatable.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.22,0:19:26.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,癌症\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Cancer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.31,0:19:29.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}世卫组织定义五大绝症包括艾滋病  恶性肿瘤\N白血病  类风湿  肌萎缩侧髓硬化症
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.31,0:19:29.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,化解全部"五大绝症"  试想一下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All five classifications. Think of it:
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.01,0:19:34.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这能治愈当代的一种最致命疾病\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}a cure for one of the deadliest diseases of our time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.92,0:19:37.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,病毒不用来害人而是是用来救人 \N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Instead of causing harm, the virus delivers a cure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.37,0:19:40.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是妙点子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's brilliant.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.18,0:19:44.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不幸的是  我们还没有完善它\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Unfortunately, we haven't perfected it yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.96,0:19:46.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是病毒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It wasn't the virus.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.27,0:19:47.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What's not?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.09,0:19:52.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,病毒让彼得生病  但并没有改变他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The virus made Peter sick but it didn't change him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.61,0:19:55.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是病毒内的基因疗法改变了他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It was the gene therapy inside the virus.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.01,0:19:58.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在纳尔维克-B菌株里加了什么才改变了他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What did you put into the NARVIK-B strain that changed him?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.51,0:19:59.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没加什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.50,0:20:02.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们还没有使用基因疗法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We hadn't introduced the gene therapy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.49,0:20:06.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,病毒里有其它东西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There is something inside this virus.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.63,0:20:10.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会找出来的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And I will find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.95,0:20:19.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你得告诉我这到底怎么回事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I need you to tell me what's really going on here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.50,0:20:22.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不关你的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It doesn't concern you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.41,0:20:26.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我唯一关心的就是你和基地的安全\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Your safety and the safety of this base is my only concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.84,0:20:29.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我被蒙在鼓里就保护不了你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I can't protect you if I'm in the dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.28,0:20:34.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不在的时候发生了很多事情\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}A lot has happened while you were away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.26,0:20:36.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜耶塞罗找到了威特博士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Balleseros found Dr. Hvit. -
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.35,0:20:39.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-什么  他是怎么...  -没事了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- What? How did he-- - it's not a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.97,0:20:41.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经把他解决了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I took care of him. -
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.07,0:20:45.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解决了他  你干了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Took care of him? How?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.25,0:20:47.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他见识了一下冰镐的厉害\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Introduced him to the business end of an ice axe.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.68,0:20:48.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并留他在冰天雪地里自生自灭\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Left him out on the ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.45,0:20:51.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底做了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What have you done?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.38,0:20:54.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你说过他的存在对我们是一个威胁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You said yourself he was a threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.90,0:20:56.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我消灭了他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I eliminated him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.21,0:20:59.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你个蠢货  难道你不知道吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You fool! Don't you see?!
