Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.52,0:36:17.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么知道是正常反应\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Normal for what?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.47,0:36:19.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的  那些猴子和他的反应一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's OK. The monkeys did the exact same thing.
