Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.97,0:36:34.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}无反应
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.86,0:36:37.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这会害死他的  艾伦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is killing him. Alan.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.20,0:36:40.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾伦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Alan!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.28,0:36:44.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-他要被淹死了  -不  不要\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- He's drowning. - No. No.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.59,0:36:46.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我们唯一能救回他的方式了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If there's any chance we could save him...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.13,0:36:49.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的体温在下降\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}His core temperature's dropping.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.12,0:36:52.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,35摄氏度\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's 95.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.97,0:36:53.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,29度\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Eighty-five.
