Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.89,0:36:56.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,24度\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Seventy-five.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.80,0:36:58.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,18度\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sixty-five.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.38,0:37:01.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,13度\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Fifty-five degrees.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.34,0:37:03.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾伦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Alan.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.97,0:37:11.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他能看见我们吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Can he see us?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.47,0:37:18.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想不能\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No. I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.65,0:37:20.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这确实起作用了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But it's something.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.97,0:37:24.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有进展了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.91,0:37:38.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疾控中心似乎有了突破性进展\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The CDC seems to have had a breakthrough.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.33,0:37:41.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉让你失望了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm sorry for disappointing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.15,0:37:45.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-请原谅我  父亲  -是我的错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Please forgive me, father-- - It's my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.34,0:37:50.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我还没有将你准备充分\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I didn't prepare you well enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.35,0:37:53.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我的失误\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I made a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.58,0:37:58.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么失误可言  只有被浪费了的机会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There are no mistakes, only opportunities wasted.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.14,0:38:01.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事不会再发生了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It won't happen again.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.36,0:38:07.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好  因为我们的时间已经不多了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Good. We don't have much time to prepare.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.18,0:38:11.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想让我做什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What do you want me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.48,0:38:15.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}First...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.70,0:38:20.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带我去看看拜耶塞罗少校的尸体\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}show me Major Balleseros' body.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.39,0:38:38.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太神奇了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.83,0:38:40.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然他的大脑活动还没完全恢复\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Brain activity isn't 100%,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.59,0:38:42.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但毕竟有所好转了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but it's a start.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.61,0:38:48.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾伦  你还好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Alan, are you OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.08,0:39:51.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就把他留在这里了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is where I left him.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.97,0:39:53.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.55,0:39:56.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我脱下了他的外套和靴子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I took his jacket and boots.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.19,0:39:57.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他走不了多远的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He couldn't have got far.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.96,0:40:11.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是被人带走了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He's been taken.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.57,0:40:13.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去找他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll go find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.31,0:40:16.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.03,0:40:18.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们晚些再处理这件事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We'll deal with this later.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.25,0:40:21.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.56,0:40:42.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Are you OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.70,0:40:45.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.01,0:40:54.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警告  有飞机驶入\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Warning: incoming flight.
