Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.86,0:41:01.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢上帝  救兵终于到了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Thank God. The cavalry's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.02,0:41:03.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How?
