Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.93,0:42:01.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,《双螺旋》  下集预告\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}On the next Helix.
